social_posts.post_text: Sometimes things aren’t clear right away. That’s where you need to be patient and persevere and see where things lead! #bigchangecomin

Possessing indomitable spirit. Having a drive for achievement regardless of upbringing or situation. Earning success in the trenches through hard work! 

Guts, Resiliency, Intensity, Tenacity=Grit 👊🏾
Work is hard. Distractions are plentiful and time is short….
Every off-season you look at what can improve on. So you come in for the new season fresh and ready to go again….
Tell me and I forget. Teach me and I remember. Involve me and I learn…
When Vessel sends you their released VLS Lux  stand bag to make your long walks that much easier…
A good life is when you assume nothing, do more, need less, smile often, dream big, laugh a lot, and realized how Blessed you are….

Today’s Mood: Cranky with a touch of Psycho…

-
#psychoobunny #psychobunnypartner
See first, think later, then test. But you always have to see first otherwise you will only see what you were expecting.
In every walk with nature, one receives far more than he seeks!
Spending that time getting creative and having fun around the greens…
What’s meant for you will find you…
